Class MonitoredMultiPartRequest

java.lang.Object

org.apache.struts2.dispatcher.multipart.MultiPartRequest
public class MonitoredMultiPartRequest
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.apache.struts2.dispatcher.multipart.MultiPartRequest

This is a multipart request handler, but utilises commons-filupload 1.2 and adds a listener to the file upload request, so that the progress can be monitor by other requests. This is a copy of JakartaMultiPartRequest with some extra code put in to handle the ProgressMonitor listener class. Strangely enough, extending JakartaMultiPartRequest and overiding the methods didnt seem to work? However, it wasnt important enough to look into why, so i just copied the code and pasted here.
